            m "I hope you'll get drunk soon"
            m "Just remember that no matter what happens, no matter what anyone says or does..."
            m "Just get drunk."
            m "Just get drunk."
            menu:
                "Just get drunk.":
                    m 4j "Drink vodnika!"
    return

